      | !{' '}That being said, one of the most important factors was the 1AM late license...
    p For many of you this will be the first time meeting one of the two of us and we can't wait to bring both of our families
      | !{' '} together on the special day. We hope to see lots of friends and family from both sides and for our southern
      | !{' '} based attendees: we wish you all the best being in a room full of northerners.
  .content-card.home-heroimage-card.home-card 
    img.home-heroimage(
      src="https://wedding-website-images-burlzad.s3.eu-west-2.amazonaws.com/images/healey-inside.jpg"
    )
